name: Universe #198
description: Universe #198 - The great artists of the universes always traveled between them. Seeking inspiration for their next piece, they never settled forever. They were in Staxei but close to leaving but it disrupted the slowly built order in the universe. 198 was there as the unstability of the universe exploded. 198 helped contain it and now helps the artists of the universe travel and find their next inspiring location.
